-- Nikkei 225 August Options Settle at 8,914.81, Data Shows
-- B y   Y o s h i a k i   N o h a r a
-- 2012-08-10T00:23:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-10/nikkei-225-august-options-settle-at-8-914-81-data-shows.html
Japan ’s Nikkei 225 August options
settled at 8,914.81, according to data compiled by Bloomberg.  The Nikkei 225 Stock Average fell 0.6 percent to 8,927.02
as of 9:21 a.m. in Tokyo. The gauge closed at 8,978.60
yesterday.  The settlement price, also known as the “special
quotation,” of Nikkei 225 options is calculated after all
stocks in the Nikkei 225 begin trading.  To contact the reporter for this story:
Yoshiaki Nohara in Tokyo at 
 ynohara1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
